    PasswordCheckerUtility
    Utility class with methods for checking the validity of passwords 1 - isValidPassword: checks if passed Strings meets five conditions * At least 6 characters long * At least one digit character * At least one uppercase alphabetic character * At least one lowercase alphabetic character * No more than two of the same character in sequence 2 - isWeakPassword: checks if password is weak (between 6 and 9 characters long inclusive) or strong (longer than 9 characters) 3 - invalidPasswords: returns list of invalid passwords from list of passwords
